keyFacts: The document is a credit account summary for World Wildlife Fund Inc, showing a Visa Platinum Plus card.
A credit line increase request from $1,000 to $20,000 was made on July 17, 2019, and was pending.
The account was opened on July 13, 2012, with a total annual income listed as $160,000 and assets of $25,000.
The account is categorized as non-transparent, VIP-41-Preferred Tier, and unsecured primary.
The document includes detailed financial metrics such as current balance, available credit, and risk scores.
